# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Giscus — GitHub Discussions integration for journal article comments
#
# Setup steps:
#   1. Ensure GitHub Discussions is enabled on your repository.
#   2. Visit https://giscus.app and configure your repository.
#   3. Copy the generated data-repo-id and data-category-id values below.
#   4. Rename this file to .env.local for local development.
#
# All four variables are required for the discussion widget to appear.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

NEXT_PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO=Shreyas-Agarwal/portfolio-next
NEXT_PUBLIC_GISCUS_REPO_ID=
NEXT_PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY=Journal Discussion
NEXT_PUBLIC_GISCUS_CATEGORY_ID=
